I know it might seem like extra effort to find POC to tell their own stories, but if you take the time to find us we're here and we're ready
Certainly, non-POC need to keep being inclusive and keep including us as characters!! By all means, please do that and feel free to ask q's.
But the conversation needs to shift over to POC being able to tell their own stories without the filter of someone else.
Now, it's much better. Some mainstream media and creators ARE trying to be more inclusive. There's conversations happening.
